text: Paraphrosylus is a genus of fly in the family Dolichopodidae. ==Species== *Paraphrosylus californicus (Harmston, 1952) *Paraphrosylus direptor (Wheeler, 1897) *Paraphrosylus grassator (Wheeler, 1897) *Paraphrosylus nigripennis (Van Duzee, 1924) *Paraphrosylus praedator (Wheeler, 1897) *Paraphrosylus wirthi (Harmston, 1951) ==References== Category:Hydrophorinae Category:Dolichopodidae genera Category:Taxa named by Theodor Becker
title: Paraphrosylus
